<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qsgbasicgeometrynode.xml">QSGBasicGeometryNode</db:link> class should not be used by itself. It is only encapsulates shared functionality between the <db:link xlink:href="qsggeometrynode.xml">QSGGeometryNode</db:link> and <db:link xlink:href="qsgclipnode.xml">QSGClipNode</db:link> classes.</db:para>
<db:note>
<db:para>All classes with QSG prefix should be used solely on the scene graph's rendering thread. See <db:link xlink:href="qtquick-visualcanvas-scenegraph.xml#scene-graph-and-rendering">Scene Graph and Rendering</db:link> for more information.</db:para>
</db:note>
</db:section>
