<db:para>Sets the geometry of this node to <db:code role="parameter">geometry</db:code>.</db:para>
<db:para>If the node has the flag <db:link xlink:href="qsgnode.xml#Flag-enum">QSGNode::OwnsGeometry</db:link> set, it will also delete the geometry object it is pointing to. This flag is not set by default.</db:para>
<db:para>If the geometry is changed without calling setGeometry() again, the user must also mark the geometry as dirty using <db:link xlink:href="qsgnode.xml#markDirty">QSGNode::markDirty</db:link>().</db:para>
